{"tid":1015711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以講下90年代-00年代初廣東省嘅治安有幾恐怖 2","createTime":"2019-02-10T08:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T04:45:25.000Z","uid":49316,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"7d765bf7c7d7f8146306a819bc8800ba2ba1cf97","tid":1015711,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個成日聽老母講深圳好多拐子佬，又多賊，羅湖城仲要有人偷器官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外廣州火車站又係好恐怖，又有飛車黨又迷暈黨。<br />\n有冇ching係嗰個年代上過去可以分享下啲經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f969c8a757dd1371cb5d623f2baab2fa9155d5b","tid":1015711,"uid":49316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講下90年代-00年代初廣東省嘅治安有幾恐怖<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/GyxCiU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/GyxCiU</a>"},{"pid":"a7196907c335d64c50f2c3f63ab076af555056bc","tid":1015711,"uid":193893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴線好撚恐怖<br />\n以前番大陸做野真係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>但係好揾，90年代中港貨櫃司機 hea 住做都月入2萬幾，仲要申請到公屋。<br />\n而家比大陸司機搶好多飯碗</blockquote>搵命搏呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同老婆講咪兩三萬，另外個兩三萬要留返黎包二奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ae1b1d8de92f5a0659092d91dd714c5fb9ec22","tid":1015711,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"高速公路拉鐵線𠝹鳩啲電單車司機個頭<br />\n之後搶野（印象中新聞有講）"},{"pid":"c3924e773478b0a513ccccb288dfd64930114693","tid":1015711,"uid":35094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"0193009b02012610839282fcce81fb77491a7ac0","tid":1015711,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"以前細個（大概90年代）返順德個邊都有播廣告小心電單車偷袋。<br />\n老豆90年代係深圳打工，星期五晚返香港，星期日上去，宿舍係布吉。<br />\n宿舍9年爆格11次，最嚴重一次係除咗$10、回鄉證同身份證外其他全部偷晒。<br />\n可能老豆唔係大隻，唔識武功，同我講唔好同個賊反抗，報公安係無用。"},{"pid":"7f3e9b04ba8d2492276bf4148bb72dbca3386740","tid":1015711,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  繼續討論"},{"pid":"21ff682fa2cbb2d12129b9cc37cb13fb93a1a70b","tid":1015711,"uid":111670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TV3v7eIfBM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTV3v7eIfBM4&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=414fec3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TV3v7eIfBM4</a>"},{"pid":"7b8c70e134aa833b44d6405cfdfae04e1e08f882","tid":1015711,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"有冇手足有多啲片share<br />\n上個post 切糕 扮手啲片精彩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029399f14a16a31efc051f2bd64d0f643b5ef5cd","tid":1015711,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"完全唔明而家啲人係用咩心態上去吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691d60008184cc91529243611dffeec0fcd3719e","tid":1015711,"uid":54516,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"029399f14a16a31efc0