gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"班youtuber &amp; content farm媒體（新假期個D）真係功不可沒，講到上去消費好正，打卡勝地。班人有得食就得，點會理治安如何，D嘢食有冇問題，又可以笑9香港人落後不思進取。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"閪多士同鳩假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班港豬次次都上去吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食哂周期元素表仲要話正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547e3f2ec6ece84ec8d151d532023d404ac16e4a","tid":1015711,"uid":118041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"就算而家都係，一出羅湖就好多冇手冇腳既乞衣<br />\n前兩個月上去，見到有個冇腳乞衣攬住隻狗乞錢<br />\n晏晝2點隻狗係訓係度；夜晚9點隻狗都係咁訓<br />\n唔知隻狗係咪畀人打左針"},{"pid":"417e22978adf8ff58c54ec2a54fbbe22f398fa8b","tid":1015711,"uid":145345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"691d60008184cc91529243611dffeec0fcd3719e","tid":1015711,"uid":54516,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"029399f14a16a31efc051f2bd64d0f643b5ef5cd","tid":1015711,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"完全唔明而家啲人係用咩心態上去吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"班youtuber &amp; content farm媒體（新假期個D）真係功不可沒，講到上去消費好正，打卡勝地。班人有得食就得，點會理治安如何，D嘢食有冇問題，又可以笑9香港人落後不思進取。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"班友算把啦<br />\n大陸係有景點既 <br />\n但同一個價我不如儲多少少錢去日本好過"},{"pid":"cc873ff0040448d55ac5f77bb8e9cae9ca98b0e5","tid":1015711,"uid":145345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"以前過羅湖橋真係好大分別<br />\n裝修無而家咁光猛<br />\n<br />\n仲有另一條橋再殘d<br />\n已經停左用<br />\n而家唔知仲有無<br />\n阿媽次次經過都會指比我睇<br />\n<br />\n同埋講佢點搵命駁游水落來"},{"pid":"25a59209b5bd404df64523e8e763da6f0bf5c427","tid":1015711,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d31a6f08cfd37624aa506ee3da8a665cbbf6a6","tid":1015711,"uid":37326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"細個同阿公返深圳搭巴士返鄉下<br />\n<br />\n中途俾架電單車閘停<br />\n<br />\n然後楂電單車果條友拎住一枝手槍指住個司機叫佢開門<br />\n<br />\n上到車打劫晒成車人， 去到我同公果度， 果陣我阿公佢戴住隻假勞力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  , 個賊叫佢除， 我阿公仲唔識死同個賊講隻野係假， 個賊即刻拎槍指住佢個頭叫我阿公唔想死就除出黎<br />\n<br />\n後尾打劫晒成車人既現金同貴重野就落車走左<br />\n<br />\n果陣我嚇到唔敢出一句聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到宜家我都唔知佢枝槍堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491cf1c3b7ca6f997261f48cfb5fdd0d54ed2d0a","tid":1015711,"uid":145345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7b8c70e134aa833b44d6405cfdfae04e1e08f882","tid":1015711,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"有冇手足有多啲片share<br />\n上個post 切糕 扮手啲片精彩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"如果有人儲開城市追擊/今日睇真d 一定有好多相關內容"},{"pid":"33b664b582f9d06a41577b7e742f8629771ac88f","tid":1015711,"uid":194609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e246b7ced168c9a8ae4af7adfd2cfe232db298e","tid":1015711,"uid":137506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"691d60008184cc91529243611dffeec0fcd3719e","tid":1015711,"uid":54516,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"029399f14a16a31efc051f2bd64d0f643b5ef5cd","tid":1015711,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"完全唔明而家啲人係用咩心態上去吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"班youtuber &amp; content farm媒體（新假期個D）真係功不可沒，講到上去消費好正，打卡勝地。班人有得食就得，點會理治