gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對支那人態度係寧願有殺錯無放過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"所以支那人真係好可憐，環境迫成佢地咁撚乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n個格就算去到發達國家都改唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"政權無能，政府冇規劃，咁既環境下生活真係好難做好人。"},{"pid":"88c90d3121609eb634afd55157fdf0670146b08f","tid":1015711,"uid":4493,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"再post:<br />\n<br />\n2012年之前仲有間中去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最初應該係幾歲時 90年代後期 大約幾個月上一次深圳同親戚食嘢買嘢<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣一過關見到五六個支那人打大交 全部好撚重手打落去有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一出口岸個個人啤住你 等機會偷呃拐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住有次去舊書城 上條行人天橋見到有個公安狂追個扒手 跑一百米速度 嗰個咁正義嘅警察可能已經死撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去高級酒樓食嘢 裏面可以有一個拖住幾個小朋友嘅丐幫周圍乞 完全冇人理 到我哋走嗰時跟到去大街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣州反而比較安全 不過都試過買到假可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扒手就周圍都有 屋企人都中過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公安會幫你搞回港安排但唔會落簿<br />\n<br />\n見過無數扒手 𠝹褲 電單車搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰時嘅深圳真係人間煉獄 不過唔算最恐怖 我個人認為美國Baltimore同San Fran個Tenderloin區至少係同級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 15年前去土耳其啱啱搞反華架旅遊巴俾人掉石真心驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰陣時去支那算係練到街頭意識 我喺美國咁耐淨係俾人打過兩次劫 兩次都成功走甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981feded698b32195f70a3a633445ae5013d2f3e","tid":1015711,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"落完和諧號行翻去羅湖口岸個段路真係好驚心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7b4ca972412249c87806b492e41380819408bb","tid":1015711,"uid":34222,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"上多D大陸唔同地方就知到底係咩一回事<br />\n北上廣深一線城市 面子工程實做得好好睇<br />\n試過去清遠 屌你個學校廁所係柯屎落屎渠 睇住隔離廁格柯咩屎<br />\n勁撚驚跌落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7-8年前去湖南張家界 遊客實劏到你一頸血 <br />\n仲未計返鄉下D市鎮  細個已聽聞飛車黨 黑的 乞衣集團<br />\n全世界D騙案係大陸都可以搵到"},{"pid":"1a6245d439524f9900f402759f74a726539448ec","tid":1015711,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15709e55a7bfc8df18d08680743c3d4cf4bfcd4d","tid":1015711,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0193009b02012610839282fcce81fb77491a7ac0","tid":1015711,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"以前細個（大概90年代）返順德個邊都有播廣告小心電單車偷袋。<br />\n老豆90年代係深圳打工，星期五晚返香港，星期日上去，宿舍係布吉。<br />\n宿舍9年爆格11次，最嚴重一次係除咗$10、回鄉證同身份證外其他全部偷晒。<br />\n可能老豆唔係大隻，唔識武功，同我講唔好同個賊反抗，報公安係無用。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"你老豆嗰時應該叫唔少雞"},{"pid":"6edc0febe7e09ecba9f4806e804a60f55ea79b38","tid":1015711,"uid":200937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b397ffc62e49d51237dd04da17c373ecbd78767d","tid":1015711,"uid":4493,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"15709e55a7bfc8df18d08680743c3d4cf4bfcd4d","