-02-11T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"以前入深圳經濟特區要查身份證，你唔係拎回鄉證、深圳戶藉人士或邊防證就唔比入。<br />\n以前有親戚住深圳關外，坐親入深圳市區巴士到檢查站都查過，不過而家檢查站都拆哂了。"},{"pid":"531ec6e72bf9ff88b274f39b7c666c4612855d90","tid":1015711,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T22:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d7771aa8e98de66bbe35a931d05929ef2b4be4","tid":1015711,"uid":52056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"十年前俾學校侷去廣州交流<br />\n晏晝個呀sir帶咗全班三幾十人去食飯，個司機就泊咗架旅遊巴入條巷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知食完飯返去泊車位見到架旅遊巴俾架私家車頂死咗出唔到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果呀sir同私家車司機傾完一輪俾咗舊錢先甩到身，事後全車人夾返買路錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩年鄉下有年紀大嘅親戚俾電單車黨搶袋搶到仆街，據講依家行路仲係趷吓趷吓咁<br />\n呀婆就喺屋企門口俾人搶玉鈪(一隻過冇扣嗰種)，隻手紅哂好彩冇斷骨<br />\n家家戶戶啲窗同天台一定有鐵籠，係講緊成寸粗厚料鐵通焊死喺幅牆/地面"},{"pid":"147057529cec9502d98d5ef22acd6530aeed3661","tid":1015711,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"留名先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daa81da07862f8c5606026f7a33cb8a9dd12dc0","tid":1015711,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"呢個post好有警世作用"},{"pid":"d64041127a54902b47581f73ff0102b0f9971256","tid":1015711,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"戲都有啦當年，深圳公路搶車劫殺案之六魔女，二奶村殺夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54de546494ab6b776d4bf642ef0e9247a19a6342","tid":1015711,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f79004768bae243523e2f0cc6a79833ecfadf731","tid":1015711,"uid"